Package spaceinvadersProject.playground

package spaceinvadersProject.playground
The package javashooter.playground contains all classes implementing and describing game levels. Main class to be subclassed here: Playground. A notable sublass that is already implelented is playground.SpaceInvadersLevel, showing an example of how to subclass Playground,
